Name: 80's OVERDRIVE
About the game: 80'S OVERDRIVE is a 2D pixel art racing game, designed to take you back in time to when 8 and 16 bit consoles and arcade games ruled the world. Compete against opponents in career mode to unlock new races, buy new cars, and upgrade them with state-of-the-art technologies! Try your skill in time attack mode and see how far you can get in this race against the clock! Create your own tracks with built-in track generator and easily share them with your friends! Features: - 2 game modes and racing track editor; - 6 retro supercars; - 8 unique visual themes; - 18 synth/retrowave music scores; - tons of retro, handcrafted, pixel-perfect joy!
